1
00:00:00,030 --> 00:00:01,535
-First time hosting.
How do you feel?

2
00:00:01,535 --> 00:00:04,525
-It's truly such an honor.
-Oh, we're so excited.

3
00:00:04,600 --> 00:00:06,627
Anyway, I had this idea
I wanted to pitch you.

4
00:00:06,627 --> 00:00:07,917
-And I would love to hear it.
-Okay, great.

5
00:00:07,917 --> 00:00:10,348
I'm your upstairs neighbor,
but I'm, like, super loud.

6
00:00:10,348 --> 00:00:11,728
You know what I mean?
I'm throwing parties.

7
00:00:11,728 --> 00:00:14,405
I'm like, "Wake up.
Get out of here!"

8
00:00:14,405 --> 00:00:17,619
-I already hate this idea.
It's the worst idea
I've ever heard.

9
00:00:17,619 --> 00:00:21,005
What do I do?
Come on, Colman,
just say you're not feeling it.

10
00:00:21,005 --> 00:00:22,969
-So what do you think?
-I love it.

11
00:00:22,969 --> 00:00:24,615
-Oh, my God. Great.
Okay, so then...

12
00:00:24,615 --> 00:00:27,828
-Why did you say you loved it?
You've really done it this time,
Colman.

13
00:00:27,828 --> 00:00:29,673
Is it too late
to switch to SNL UK?

14
00:00:29,673 --> 00:00:31,965
The idea is getting worse
by the second.

15
00:00:31,965 --> 00:00:34,703
Is she doing Soulja Boy?

16
00:00:34,988 --> 00:00:37,443
-Maybe if I tell someone
she tried to kiss me,
she'll get fired.

17
00:00:37,443 --> 00:00:39,069
I never thought I'd be
jealous of dead people.

18
00:00:39,069 --> 00:00:41,440
The sketch involves
hobby horses now?

19
00:00:41,440 --> 00:00:43,677
Please, God, strike me down.

20
00:00:43,677 --> 00:00:47,884
This is so annoying.
And that's coming from someone
who spent his whole life
around theater people.

21
00:00:47,884 --> 00:00:51,436
Good lord, how did
we get to black Captain Hook?

22
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:54,974
-You got this, Colman.
Just say no.

23
00:00:54,974 --> 00:00:58,250
-So basically, that's it.
What do you think?
I mean, you could say no.

24
00:00:58,250 --> 00:01:01,811
-I-I-I-I just feel like, ah...

25
00:01:01,811 --> 00:01:06,206
maybe.
I wonder if, uh...

26
00:01:06,617 --> 00:01:08,825
It's the best thing
I've ever heard.

27
00:01:08,825 --> 00:01:10,608
We are absolutely doing this.

28
00:01:10,608 --> 00:01:13,421
-Yes! Oh, my God, I knew it.

